{"tid":2150434,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尼日爾野生園區八遊客被槍殺","createTime":"2020-08-11T02:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T03:10:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13d38dab533438f63581461dd7e7c9e20ba0817b","tid":2150434,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T02:50:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200811/NZ5POBNKSYUO3L3FWWNNQE5X2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200811%2FNZ5POBNKSYUO3L3FWWNNQE5X2M%2F&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lD2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=dc960a6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200811%2FNZ5POBNKSYUO3L3FWWNNQE5X2M%2F&h=5a39f1a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200811/NZ5POBNKSYUO3L3FWWNNQE5X2M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n尼日爾野生園區八遊客被槍殺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9-6TpTWs9Htspgg92e-z-RWXCQ0=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EY6X6TORLNP3VTZ2J5WL2Z7OB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9-6TpTWs9Htspgg92e-z-RWXCQ0%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEY6X6TORLNP3VTZ2J5WL2Z7OB4.jpg&h=2e9d4293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國多名援助人員乘坐的車嚴重損毀。<br />\n<br />\n恐怖分子肆虐的西非尼日爾前日發生槍擊案，一批槍手騎電單車突擊長頸鹿園區，殺害六名法國人道援助人員，司機和導遊亦遭殃，暫時未有組織承認責任。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n車輛燒焦 遺留彈孔<br />\n<br />\n槍擊案於當地時間前日中午11時半於庫雷地區東部一個保護園區內發生，眾人被發現伏屍路邊，法國電視台播出片段可見現場一輛相信是他們乘搭的四驅車，已被燒焦，車身有不少彈孔。出事保護園區相距首都尼亞美65公里，園內育有尼日爾最後一批獨有的淺色長頸鹿，因而成為旅遊熱點。<br />\n<br />\n事後，法國人道救援組織。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n尼日爾曾屬法國殖民地，近期涉及博科聖地及親伊斯蘭國（IS）。。。。。。。。。列作恐怖主義謀殺案處理。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司"},{"pid":"81160d2b50b13cd0479b5659b8bd4730b0ba4339","tid":2150434,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T02:52:14.000Z","msg":"盜獵者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f457c2ed5c723579044be15280ab07eb5b49fdf7","tid":2150434,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T02:54:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b49123c2ff7feb339eca4f6238e2b4f6b5569464","tid":2150434,"uid":71433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f457c2ed5c723579044be15280ab07eb5b49fdf7","tid":2150434,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T02:54:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"有到風班恐怖份子有拍片<br />\n你打去問問"}]}